results.name: Number of abelian subgroups of the group SL(2, Z(n)), counting conjugates as distinct.
program: (GAP) Concatenation([1], List([2..10], n->Sum( Filtered( ConjugacyClassesSubgroups( SL(2, Integers mod n)), x->IsAbelian( Representative(x))), Size)));
results.author: _Andrew Howroyd_, Jul 06 2018
